@node "Future_Ideas" "The Future"
@TOC "MAIN"

@{U}@{B}So what does the future hold?@{UU}@{UB}


To be honest, I don't know. I will continue to support the Amiga and
Speccy as I think they are simply the two finest machines I have used.

I may try and update the INSTALL script a little bit to get round the
problem of POKEs being overwritten.

I may also try and update it to support other "launchers".. I only
use ToolsDaemon, so that's why it was supported here, but if I find
any launchers which have a "text based" config file, then I may
update it.

Basically, if you can think of anything you'd like to see on the
Speccy-Amiga side, let me know,,, I am NOT a programmer, but if
you think it could be done in AREXX or INSTALLER, @{"get in touch" link "Call_ME"}.
I also scan, and make Klondike cardsets, convert Speccy loading screen$
to IFF/GIF formats, and any other hobbies/projects which enter my
diseased mind :-)

@endnode

