@node "Replace" "Replace docs. Converted to GUIDE"
@TOC "MAIN"



                   Information for 'Replace'


Need's dos.library V37 or better !!

******************************************************************************

  I do not take any responsibility for what you do with this program.

******************************************************************************

Replace is a Programm, to replace ASCII-Text in File's with other ASCII-Text's.


Replace [D] "Path/Filepattern" "Target-Dir/" "Old_Text" "New_Text"

[D]	When Present, the File's, which were Changed and Save'd to the
	Target-Dir, will be deleted.


